These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, july, november, april, december, october, march
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Birthday   | march | november | december | january | april | july | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: whist, go, monopoly, bridge, poker, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing bridge and the person playing whist##2
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg | whist | monopoly | bridge | go | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
House: gothic-revival, palace, cape-cod, townhouse, colonial, craftsman, ranch-style
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the colonial house is between the craftsman house and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| House   | ranch-style | craftsman | colonial | palace | gothic-revival | cape-cod | townhouse |

