.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, fonseca, pall-mall, havana, aristoff, cain, prince
1. the prince-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the prince-smoker is in the middle##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is the pall-mall-smoker##1
8. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | cain | fonseca | havana | prince | aristoff | bolivar | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
City: nizza, colone, hamburg, prague, new-york, liverpool, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to new-york##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to prague is the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to colone##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| City   | edinburgh | prague | liverpool | new-york | hamburg | colone | nizza |

