4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is rowing##2
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |    4    |       5       |      6       |    7    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | basketball | rugby | rowing | handball | tennis | parkour |

