.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, poppy, rose, dahlia, lily, zinnia
1. the person who growsiris is between the person who growslily and the person who growsdahlia##2
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |    3    |    4    |     5     |    6    |     7     |
| Flower   | orchid | zinnia | poppy | rose | lily | iris | dahlia |

