1. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the cain-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the game-smoker##2
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the havana-smoker##2
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |  7   |
| Cigar   | game | cain | swisher | bluemaster | dunhill | pall-mall | havana |

