2. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating apple and the person eating peas##2
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |     3     |      4      |      5      |   6    |      7       |
| Food   | grapefruit | pineapple | zucchini | cauliflower | apple | cranberry | peas |

