.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, november, september, february, march, april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in february##2
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Birthday   | april | july | september | october | march | february | november |

