3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |   3    |   4    |   5    |   6    |    7     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | skydiving | cooking | singing | reading | camping | collecting |

