2. the fan house is on the far left##1
3. the fan pop is on the left of the fan r&b##1
4. the fan indie is on the right of the fan d&b##1
5. the fan indie is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5   |    6     |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house | rock | pop | r&b | salsa | d&b | indie |

